{"tid":1426362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搵到港共政府弱點 就係遍地開花式集會","createTime":"2019-08-07T02:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T04:26:00.000Z","uid":199926,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2454089621f82881a2c6eadea4cc10d4ae7834df","tid":1426362,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:03:48.000Z","msg":"805係我廿幾年人以黎<br />\n第一次見到成條彌敦道所有鋪頭落晒閘商場封晒<br />\n想搵個商場去洗手間嘆下冷氣都搵唔到<br />\n想搵711買支水都冇開<br />\n<br />\n如果香港三日唔埋兩日都有遍地開花式既各區集會<br />\n而啲商舖商場都唔敢開門落晒閘<br />\n唔知香港個經濟損失會有幾慘重呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4ecb371391bda6c4cd0c11dc30f09d8d0226c6","tid":1426362,"uid":522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:04:17.000Z","msg":"年青人都買唔到樓既經濟 仲要黎做乜?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e312d04c71dc32c2aec9423136076011b847d291","tid":1426362,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:04:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ec13efb09161d5b6f1ae8b9738c1aafe352babf","tid":1426362,"uid":3571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:05:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58ad9a14c779a234ea5ca1b2cd757b02b9a74d60","tid":1426362,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ec13efb09161d5b6f1ae8b9738c1aafe352babf","tid":1426362,"uid":3571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:05:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:08:15.000Z","msg":"只要記住一有示威遊行集會 啲商舖就會落閘<br />\n大家唔想邊度有生意做就去邊度集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6389e6aa0cdaa02b2d5a6e01cc06d62d98c65517","tid":1426362,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c4ecb371391bda6c4cd0c11dc30f09d8d0226c6","tid":1426362,"uid":522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"c